00:23:44,850 --> 00:23:45,832
we can know for sure

603
00:23:45,833 --> 00:23:47,434
about life 20 years

604
00:23:47,435 --> 00:23:50,975
after people are gone

605
00:23:51,010 --> 00:23:54,516
because there's one spot

606
00:23:54,517 --> 00:23:56,155
on the globe

607
00:23:56,190 --> 00:24:01,258
Where it's already happened.

608
00:24:22,432 --> 00:24:23,259
It's 20 years

609
00:24:23,294 --> 00:24:29,073
into a life after people.

