00:24:48,104 --> 00:24:49,636
Animals that have long avoided

618
00:24:49,637 --> 00:24:51,539
human population centers

619
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:53,342
now return to make new homes

620
00:24:53,343 --> 00:24:59,823
among the decaying walls.

621
00:24:59,858 --> 00:25:02,056
How do we know this?

622
00:25:02,057 --> 00:25:02,898
Because there's one place

623
00:25:02,899 --> 00:25:04,400
in the world

624
00:25:04,401 --> 00:25:11,042
where it's already happened.

625
00:25:11,112 --> 00:25:11,572
We're standing

626
00:25:11,573 --> 00:25:13,410
in the central square

627
00:25:13,445 --> 00:25:15,248
of Pripyat, Ukraine,

628
00:25:15,249 --> 00:25:16,715
the city that was once

629
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:18,182
the most modern city

630
00:25:18,183 --> 00:25:23,161
in the former Soviet Union.

631
00:25:25,535 --> 00:25:27,037
For 20 years now,

632
00:25:27,038 --> 00:25:27,734
this city

633
00:25:27,769 --> 00:25:29,701
has been sitting abandoned,

634
00:25:29,702 --> 00:25:31,173
and it really gives you

635
00:25:31,175 --> 00:25:33,809
a picture of what would happen

636
00:25:33,844 --> 00:25:35,481
if people are removed

637
00:25:35,516 --> 00:25:36,282
from a place

638
00:25:36,283 --> 00:25:45,297
of normal civilization.

639
00:25:45,332 --> 00:25:46,429
Evacuated after

640
00:25:46,430 --> 00:25:49,434
the Chernobyl nuclear disaster,

641
00:25:49,469 --> 00:25:50,074
Pripyat went

642
00:25:50,076 --> 00:25:55,414
from a city of 50,000

643
00:25:55,415 --> 00:26:10,133
to ghost town overnight.

644
00:26:10,168 --> 00:26:12,311
Dust-covered school rooms remain

645
00:26:12,346 --> 00:26:13,473
as students left them

646
00:26:13,474 --> 00:26:26,029
just over 20 years ago.

647
00:26:26,064 --> 00:26:28,237
vegetation pries apart masonry

648
00:26:28,238 --> 00:26:37,252
as it crawls over buildings.

649
00:26:37,287 --> 00:26:38,454
An amusement park

650
00:26:38,455 --> 00:26:39,421
scheduled to open

651
00:26:39,456 --> 00:26:40,857
four days after the date

652
00:26:40,858 --> 00:26:42,390
of the accident

