00:30:05,193 --> 00:30:06,319
The original amounts

736
00:30:06,354 --> 00:30:08,497
of radioactivity were sufficient

737
00:30:08,532 --> 00:30:09,859
to kill all of the wildlife

738
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:15,174
in the region as well.

739
00:30:15,209 --> 00:30:16,510
But now we see a resurgence

740
00:30:16,545 --> 00:30:25,454
of the wildlife.

