00:30:25,456 --> 00:30:27,228
As an example of how wildlife

742
00:30:27,263 --> 00:30:29,491
has prospered here,

743
00:30:29,492 --> 00:30:31,294
we see, here, we have an antler

744
00:30:31,295 --> 00:30:33,268
from a red deer and, obviously,

745
00:30:33,303 --> 00:30:34,265
a fairly large

746
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:38,877
and healthy red deer.

