00:30:38,878 --> 00:30:40,079
Red deer are hardly found

748
00:30:40,114 --> 00:30:41,811
in any other areas

749
00:30:41,812 --> 00:30:42,683
in this region

750
00:30:42,684 --> 00:30:44,586
and the Chernobyl zone

751
00:30:44,587 --> 00:30:45,383
is the only place

752
00:30:45,418 --> 00:30:47,421
that you'll find populations

753
00:30:47,456 --> 00:30:51,062
of red deer.

754
00:30:51,097 --> 00:30:53,130
We also find russian wild boars

755
00:30:53,131 --> 00:30:55,204
that the populations in the zone

756
00:30:55,239 --> 00:30:57,236
are 10 to 15 times higher

757
00:30:57,237 --> 00:30:58,378
than they are outside

758
00:30:58,379 --> 00:31:07,393
of the zone.

