00:31:14,736 --> 00:31:16,568
while their parents worked.

765
00:31:16,569 --> 00:31:17,510
But after that night

766
00:31:17,511 --> 00:31:19,308
in april 1986,

767
00:31:19,343 --> 00:31:23,820
they never returned.

