00:33:49,218 --> 00:33:51,005
one that says that life

826
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:52,793
is much more resilient

827
00:33:52,794 --> 00:33:54,927
than what we thought possible.

828
00:33:54,928 --> 00:33:57,671
That in the absence of man,

829
00:33:57,672 --> 00:33:59,424
that life will continue

830
00:33:59,459 --> 00:34:02,451
and that life will thrive

831
00:34:02,486 --> 00:34:05,443
and that the legacy of life

